Society.Relationships:
Many ice archons were known to serve [[Cryonax]], the evil [[archomental]] of elemental ice.{{cite book/Heroes of the Elemental Chaos|25, 28}} Those that lived in Soulfreeze served the [[demon lord]] [[Aseroth]].{{Cite dragon/367/Hall of the Frostmaiden|62}}

Rimehammers were also known to serve creatures with ties to the Elemental Chaos, such as [[frost giant]]s, frostshapers, and [[frost titan]]s. But elemental archons in general had no aversions to working with creatures of other elements, so one could even see rimehammers working for such unlikely masters as [[fire giant]]s and [[efreeti]].

Among their fellow archons, ice archons worked better with [[earth archon]]s than [[fire archon|fire ones]], due to the former having similar approaches to warfare. And they were sometimes seen working alongside [[air archon]]s.
